Package com.doa.ui

Class DoaUIContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.doa.engine.DoaObject
      • com.doa.ui.DoaUIComponent
        • com.doa.ui.DoaUIContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoaPanel
    public abstract class DoaUIContainer
extends DoaUIComponent
    DoaUIContainer is the root of the UI component container hierarchy. Every UI component container have DoaUIContainer as a superclass. It is encouraged to add DoaUIComponents to DoaUIContainers after instantiating them. When a UI component container becomes active, all components the container holds also become active.
    Since:
    DoaEngine 2.3
    Version:
    2.5
    Author:
